Summary: My patrol partner and I noticed these. The objects did not move, dissipate, or disappear. The contrails dissipated. The two objects remained in a hover.

divs: Sighting DetailsWe were Northbound on a Hemet street. We were on a routine volunteer patrol for Hemet PD. Two contrails Part of a contrail. The two objects were hovering. We wondered what they were. We turned on a cross street.
